---
title: Double Crispy Serrano Tricolore Bruschetta with Caramelised Red Onion and Rocket Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Double Crispy Serrano Tricolore Bruschetta in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
